{"tid":286102,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇手畜叫Angus/安格斯？？？","createTime":"2017-06-16T10:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T17:37:52.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1299f09d334b6e2e532ea8d7774da852e4d95f9d","tid":286102,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"父親節禮物! 為每位叫Angus的你免費送上安格斯漢堡<br />\n<br />\n6月18日父親節當天，每位香港永久性居民身份證上印有 「Angus」 或 「安格斯」的顧客，只需向職員出示香港永久性居民身份證，即可免費獲得「芝味蘑菇安格斯」或「泰脆洋蔥安格斯」一客！<br />\n<br />\n免費換領安格斯漢堡的條款及細則：<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 優惠只限2017年6月18日當天享用<br />\n<br />\n&middot; 顧客必須向職員出示印有「Angus」 或 「安格斯」名字的香港永久性居民身份證作核實，方可換領「芝味蘑菇安格斯」或「泰脆洋蔥安格斯」一客<br />\n<br />\n老麥良心企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7c379e410f030eb74edf529102f321adcf24cf","tid":286102,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"邊個身份證叫安格斯 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我請佢食多個包又點話 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中資後麥記都戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"eb92517d60eebfb942e48b5a69a01faebb5d5a9b","tid":286102,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5de043ed8776f73ef55182dbd2b09beb024e962","tid":286102,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l83qb0k1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl83qb0k1&h=1c6c2a25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a579e12346ef5d71f4a87908c1768879de80c81c","tid":286102,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個身份證叫安格斯 <br />\n<br />\n<img